These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, nurse, scientist, manager
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, cabbage, pomegranate, raspberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking, hiking, writing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, april, october, june
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, hedgehog, lizard
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, pink, blood-red, aquamarine
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, jet-ski, snowmobile
 1. the person eating broccoli is between the librarian and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 2. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the nurse##1
 6. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person driving the bus and the owner of the lizard##2
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 9. the person eating raspberry is the person who's birthday is in february##1
10. the person who likes pink is the person eating cabbage##1
11. the person who likes aquamarine is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the scientist##1
13. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
14. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
15. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Job      | scientist        | manager     | nurse | librarian      |
| Food          | pomegranate | cabbage    | broccoli      | raspberry  |
| Hobby         | filmmaking  | writing    | camping       | hiking     |
| Birthday   | october        | june       | april          | february |
| Pet           | hedgehog    | chinchilla | goldfish      | lizard     |
| Color         | lilac   | pink   | blood-red      | aquamarine    |
| Transport     | bike        | bus        | snowmobile    | jet-ski    |

