.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, mirinda
House: townhouse, wooden, gothic-revival, farmhouse
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, baccarat, fonseca, dannemann
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, mystery, scientific, sports
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, horse, lizard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, funk, hip-hop, gospel
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, roller, trike
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 4. the fan of hip-hop is the owner of the fish##1
 5. the person watching mystery movies is the farmhouse house##1
 6. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 8. the wooden house is the person driving the bike##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is the dannemann-smoker##1
10. the townhouse house is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
12. the townhouse house is between the person driving the roller and the gothic-revival house##2
13. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
14. the fan of funk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
15. the person driving the trike is on the left of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |       4       |
